title: Belt configuration

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a belt configuration, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is an enlarged top perspective view of the belt configuration showing our new design;
FIG. 2 is an enlarged top plan view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a reduced front view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a reduced right side view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a reduced left side view thereof;
FIG. 6 is a reduced rear view thereof; and,
FIG. 7 is an enlarged top perspective view thereof.

The broken line showing of portions of the belt configuration is included for the purpose of illustrating only and forms no part of the claimed design. Also, all surfaces not shown form no part of the claimed design.
